video.title: Family Reunion
video.synopsis: When the McKellan family moves from Seattle to small-town Georgia, life down South — and traditional grandparents — challenge their big-city ways.

episodes.synopsis: The McKellans head to a family reunion at M'Dear and Grandpa's house, where Moz, Cocoa and the kids consider a simpler life away from city comforts.
episodes.title: Remember How This All Started?

episodes.synopsis: While cleaning out the attic, Mazzi and Shaka find M'Dear's private mementos from a famous singer — a discovery that stirs up drama with Grandpa.
episodes.title: Remember Charlie Wilson?

episodes.synopsis: When Moz gifts the kids go-karts, Cocoa is less than thrilled. Jade uses an app to try and outsmart M'Dear, an undisputed "Bible champion."
episodes.title: Remember Vacation Bible School?

episodes.synopsis: Cocoa's unconventional beliefs shock M'Dear's Bible-study group. Jade uses sisterly bonding for quality time with Drew — until she forgets about Ami.
episodes.title: Remember When I Lost My Sister?

episodes.synopsis: The family's religious role model, Auntie Grace, reveals her secret passion. When a kitchen fire erupts, Moz teaches the kids the importance of honesty.
episodes.title: Remember Grace Under Fire?

episodes.synopsis: The McKellans recall a cross-country move to Georgia that was packed with misadventure, from a weird proposal and a creepy ritual to a frisky raccoon.
episodes.title: Remember That Crazy Road Trip?

episodes.synopsis: As the kids start a new school year, Jade takes a stand against a strict dress code, Mazzi opts to redo fourth grade and Shaka eyes a potential crush.
episodes.title: Remember the First Day of School?

episodes.synopsis: When Jade competes in a pageant, she recruits a former beauty queen to be her coach. Meanwhile, Mazzi tests his "macho" abilities to impress Moz.
episodes.title: Remember Macho Mazzi?

episodes.synopsis: After M'Dear shares the family's rich history with the kids, Moz and Cocoa are inspired to carry on the tradition.
episodes.title: Remember Black Elvis?

episodes.synopsis: M'Dear introduces Jade to a new boy, and Mazzi and Shaka find a job to earn extra money. But an encounter with a cop soon has the family on edge.
episodes.title: Remember When Our Boys Became Men?

episodes.synopsis: To go on a school trip, Jade is forced to ace math as her teacher starts dating Daniel. Shaka's step team tryout fires up Cocoa's competitive streak.
episodes.title: Remember the Dance Battle?

episodes.synopsis: Jade manages Mazzi's music group, which becomes a hit at church. As Ami works to overcome her fear of getting baptized, Moz has a spiritual awakening.
episodes.title: Remember When Daddy Came Home?

episodes.synopsis: Before Moz and Cocoa say "I do" again, Shaka is tasked with keeping the ring, Cocoa confronts her mother and Daniel makes a sacrifice.
episodes.title: Remember Our Parents' Wedding?

episodes.synopsis: Jade faces criticism over a new crush. Moz and Mazzi try to keep their cool in a basketball game when a rival trash-talks them ... until M'Dear steps in.
episodes.title: Remember When Jade Was Down with the Swirl?

episodes.synopsis: An encounter with a bully inspires Shaka to try martial arts. To earn money for concert tickets, Jade gets ambitious about babysitting.
episodes.title: Remember When Shaka Got Beat Up?

episodes.synopsis: Jade searches for her singing voice and befriends an aspiring rapper-producer. Pressed for time, Mazzi asks M'Dear for help with a school project.
episodes.title: Remember the G Club?

episodes.synopsis: Jade and Aunt Maybelle bring dates to meet the family. Cocoa looks into an opportunity for her jewelry line, and M'Dear conducts an interrogation.
episodes.title: Remember Cousin Kenya?

episodes.synopsis: Shaka snoops into Jade's diary and uses a secret to blackmail her — until she gets dirt on him. M'Dear steals Moz's thunder on a sports talk show.
episodes.title: Remember M'dear's Fifteen Minutes?

episodes.synopsis: Jade hosts a masquerade party for her 15th birthday so she can sneak someone in. Meanwhile, Moz and Cocoa get a reality check about their finances.
episodes.title: Remember When the Party Was Over?

episodes.synopsis: Mazzi and Uncle Daniel set their sights on the same woman. M'Dear becomes obsessed with bingo. An injured Moz considers a return to football.
episodes.title: Remember Mazzi's First Love?

episodes.synopsis: A heartbroken Jade joins Shaka’s dojo while Mazzi learns to strike back at a bully. Moz looks to repair Cocoa's car on his own, but M'Dear interferes.
episodes.title: Remember When Jade Broke a Nail?

episodes.synopsis: To promote her jewelry line, Cocoa appears on a reality show. M’Dear looks to spice up her marriage. Moz spies on Jade when she starts dating a new guy.
episodes.title: Remember When Cocoa Was a Housewife?

episodes.synopsis: When a historic hotel is on the verge of being demolished, M'Dear chains herself to the building in protest and recalls meeting various icons.
episodes.title: Remember When M'Dear Changed History?

episodes.synopsis: Shaka deals with rejection. A risqué sculpture of Moz and Cocoa drives M'Dear mad. Jade learns her history after receiving her DNA test results.
episodes.title: Remember the False Idol?

episodes.synopsis: Jade gives M'Dear a stylish makeover. Moz and Cocoa stress about funds when Shaka gets into a gifted science program.
episodes.title: Remember When Shaka Did the Robot?

episodes.synopsis: With Principal Glass' untimely passing, the McKellans teach the kids about the circle of life. Mark Curry guest stars in his final episode.
episodes.title: Remember When the Glass Passed?

episodes.synopsis: M'Dear takes over Cocoa's Zumba ministry to win a bet. A classmate makes racially insensitive comments when Jade wins a fashion contest.
episodes.title: Remember When Cocoa Found Her Calling?

episodes.synopsis: Despite M'Dear's warnings, the McKellan kids play with a Ouija board that turns their Halloween into a strange — and spooky — night.
episodes.title: Remember When the Trick Wasn’t a Treat?

episodes.synopsis: When M'Dear secures the lead role in Cocoa's musical, Jade pretends she's the star on social media. Cousin Barron reveals his truth to the family.
episodes.title: Remember When M'Dear Stole the Show?

episodes.synopsis: A slippery accident lands Jade and the kids in Grown City, a place where no children exist. But Jade learns that being an adult isn't what it seems.
episodes.title: Remember When Jade Thought She Was Grown?

episodes.synopsis: Jade attempts to go vegan. Cocoa meets Shaka's girlfriend. A trip to an escape room with Mazzi brings up old, painful memories for M'Dear.
episodes.title: Remember the Story M’Dear Hates to Tell?

episodes.synopsis: On Valentine's Day, Shaka prepares for a special moment while Cocoa and Moz attempt a romantic evening alone. Elsewhere, challenges arise for Daniel.
episodes.title: Remember My Funny Valentine?

episodes.synopsis: Ahead of a big interview, Cocoa scrambles to handle every crisis thrown her way. Jade struggles with heartache. Mazzi and Shaka start a war of pranks.
episodes.title: Remember When Cocoa Did It All?

episodes.synopsis: A surprise birthday party for M'Dear turns her mood around. The kids find a reason to help out with money. Moz and Cocoa share a special announcement.
episodes.title: Remember M'Dear's Roast?
